  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">What Works Hub for Global Education</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The What Works Hub will ensure UK leadership on global education evidence and advice. It will respond to the Ministerial action plan on girls education and the urgent demand from governments for rapid reform to address the learning crisis. The hub will support governments to address the C-19 crisis and build back better to ensure teachers are equiped to deliver skills for the future. Through thought leadership, conveing and provision of global goods it will contribute to the UK target of 50M girls and boys learning with a focus on the most marginalised.</narrative>
  </description>
